metadata.name: Michel Gondry
metadata.description:
Michel Gondry "spooky hand" 2006

This photoshoot was done while Michel Gondry was promoting the movie "The Science of Sleep" in Mexico City.

This photo was taken with my fujifil FinePix S3Pro
and processed in black and white on Lr.

2848 x 4256 px // 300dpi // 12.1 mb // .jpg

First collector can claim a signed A4 physical print.

Minted in June 2022 by @VictorAyala.
